To use:

1. Sign up for a twilio account
2. Get a twilio SMS number
3. Deploy this to heroku or dokku
4. Obtain an access token via [these instructions](http://blog.paulshi.me/technical/2013/11/27/Philips-Hue-Remote-API-Explained.html)
5. configure your app with environment variables `HUE_ACCESS_TOKEN` and `LIGHT_ID`
4. In the request url, put your web address with the path /sms
5. Text a color to your sms number

